       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI77202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI77202.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Anulaçăo de Factura                                        *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI77202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5012 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3600 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV7720.
       COPY COCV7721.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT5012 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5012'.
           05 CON-COVT3600 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3600'.
           05 CON-1        PIC X(01) VALUE '1'.
           05 CON-2        PIC X(01) VALUE '2'.
           05 CON-3        PIC X(01) VALUE '3'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI77202'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI77202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT      TO COCV7720-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7720-ASE                 TO COCV7721-ASE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1500-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 1500-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1500-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1500-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1500-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7720-REFINVOICE EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-S
               MOVE COCK0001-STATUS-NAOEMIT  TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                        TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       1500-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-ADE       TO COCV7721-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2160-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2160-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * Obtem dados modificaçăo
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2160-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2160-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV7720-REFINVOICE   TO COCD5012-GREFINV.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT
                       NIDINVOICE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CSTATUS
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GREFINV
                     , DPAG
                     , CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET
                     , GREFNCR
                     , DDATEMINCR
                     , CMOTANU
                     , CTIPANU
                     , NTOTNCR
                     , NTAXNCR
                 INTO
                       :COCD5012-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD5012-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD5012-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD5012-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD5012-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD5012-CUSERID
                     , :COCD5012-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD5012-GREFINV
                     , :COCD5012-DPAG
                     , :COCD5012-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD5012-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD5012-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD5012-NOTAS
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXRET
                     , :COCD5012-GREFNCR
                     , :COCD5012-DDATEMINCR
                     , :COCD5012-CMOTANU
                     , :COCD5012-CTIPANU
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTNCR
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXNCR
                  FROM  COVT5012_INVOICES
                 WHERE  GREFINV     = :COCD5012-GREFINV
                   AND  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5012  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Só pode anular a factura se o status for   ---*
      *--- 9 - Pendente de Emissăo de Nota de Crédito ---*
      *--------------------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF COCD5012-CSTATUS = COCK0002-CSTATUS-PENC
                    CONTINUE
                 ELSE
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-ANUL-NAO-PODE
                      TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-MSG
                       MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                         TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE COCD5012-NIDINVOICE    TO COCV7721-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCV7721-NIDPROJECTO
                 MOVE COCD5012-GCLIENTE      TO COCV7721-GCLIENTE
                 MOVE COCD5012-DDATAINSER    TO COCV7721-DDATAINSER
                 MOVE COCD5012-DDATAEMISS    TO COCV7721-DDATAEMISS
                 MOVE COCD5012-DDATAEMIS2    TO COCV7721-DDATAEMIS2
                 MOVE COCD5012-DDATEDUE      TO COCV7721-DDATEDUE
                 MOVE COCD5012-CPRAZO        TO COCV7721-CPRAZO
                 MOVE COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO COCV7721-NTOTALAMOUNT
                 MOVE COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV7721-NTAXAMOUNT
                 MOVE COCD5012-GDESCINVOICE  TO COCV7721-GDESCINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD5012-CSTATUS       TO COCV7721-CSTATUS
                 MOVE COCD5012-GREFINV       TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE
                 MOVE COCD5012-DPAG          TO COCV7721-DDATEPAG
                 MOVE COCD5012-CMOEDA        TO COCV7721-CMOEDA
                 MOVE COCD5012-CIMPOSTO      TO COCV7721-CIMPOSTO
                 MOVE COCD5012-NOTAS         TO COCV7721-NOTAS
      **R        MOVE COCD5012-NTOTPAG       TO COCV7721-NVALREC
      **R        MOVE COCD5012-NTAXPAG       TO COCV7721-NTAXREC
                 MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCV7721-NVALREC
                 MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCV7721-NTAXREC
                 COMPUTE COCV7721-NVALTOT = COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT +
                                            COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT
                 MOVE COCD5012-GREFNCR       TO COCV7721-REFNCR
                 MOVE COCD5012-DDATEMINCR    TO COCV7721-DDATEMINCR
                 MOVE COCD5012-CMOTANU       TO COCV7721-CMOTANU
                 MOVE COCD5012-CTIPANU       TO COCV7721-CTIPANU
                 MOVE COCD5012-NTOTNCR       TO COCV7721-NTOTNCR
                 MOVE COCD5012-NTAXNCR       TO COCV7721-NTAXNCR

              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-REFINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2160-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV7721-GDESCINVOICE'   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV7721-GDESCINVOICE    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'SQLCODE              '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  SQLCODE                  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7721-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV7721-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7721-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
